        "category": "Expression of Ideas",
        "skill": "Transitions",
        "text": "Exercise provides many health benefits. It strengthens the heart and muscles. ______, regular physical activity can improve mental health by reducing stress and anxiety.\n\nWhich choice completes the text with the most logical transition?",
        "choices": [
