      {
        "id": "r_easy_15",
        "category": "Information and Ideas",
        "skill": "Central Ideas",
        "text": "Recycling programs help reduce waste sent to landfills. Materials like paper, plastic, glass, and metal can be processed and made into new products. This not only conserves natural resources but also saves energy compared to manufacturing items from raw materials.\n\nWhich choice best states the main idea of the text?",
        "choices": [
