          "Recycling provides environmental and resource benefits.",
          "Only paper and plastic can be recycled effectively.",
          "Landfills are the best place to dispose of waste."
        ],
        "correct": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "r_easy_16",
        "category": "Craft and Structure",
        "skill": "Words in Context",
        "text": "The documentary filmmaker's work was praised for its ______ portrayal of life in remote villages, capturing authentic moments without staging or manipulation.\n\nWhich choice completes the text with the most logical and precise word or phrase?",
        "choices": [
