          "All vaccines work in exactly the same way."
        ],
        "correct": 2
      },
      {
        "id": "r_easy_19",
        "category": "Craft and Structure",
        "skill": "Words in Context",
        "text": "The negotiator's ______ approach helped both parties reach a compromise without either side feeling they had lost too much ground.\n\nWhich choice completes the text with the most logical and precise word or phrase?",
