      {
        "id": "r_med_9",
        "category": "Information and Ideas",
        "skill": "Command of Evidence (Quantitative)",
        "text": "A study examined reading habits across different age groups:\n\nAge Group | Books Read Per Year\n18-29: 12\n30-49: 15\n50-64: 18\n65+: 23\n\nWhich choice most effectively uses data from the table to support the claim that older adults read more books than younger adults?",
        "choices": [
