        "category": "Standard English Conventions",
        "skill": "Boundaries",
        "text": "The ancient city of Petra, located in modern-day Jordan, ______ an architectural marvel featuring elaborate buildings carved directly into rock faces.\n\nWhich choice completes the text so that it conforms to the conventions of Standard English?",
