        "category": "Information and Ideas",
        "skill": "Inferences",
        "text": "Studies have shown that bilingual individuals often perform better on tasks requiring multitasking and attention control. Researchers believe this advantage comes from constantly managing two language systems, which exercises the brain's executive functions.\n\nWhich conclusion is most strongly supported by the text?",
